reviewText: Hilarious video.  We have watched over and over!
Funny and some actual golf plays!!

During a 20 year class reunion, 4 friends and their spouses/girlfriend get together for a few days and reminiscence about old times and talk about what they are doing today. Much of the film is four guys talking on the golf course with formula slapstick comedy. The girls all get together and are envious of the 22 year old wife.

The film was rather trite. The ending brings things together in an attempt to make it into a feel good romance, but lands short of the cup.

Guide No swearing or nudity. Near sex.

Not a great movie, but fun.  I love Chris Gauthier, who played Vincent on Eureka (my favorite TV show) and I just Love him in this film!!
His talent just shines through and really makes this film. You just want to give him a hug <3

If you just play in charity golf scambles... you have met all these characters somewhere along the line. Great movie for
any golfing reunion.
If you are a golf fan or this want to see a comedy with a bit if "drama," this this movie out.
I found this seller very good concerning the time of arrival and condition of the book.(Rees Howells: Intercessor)
